translation.Name: Kuwait Note #3
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: I, the benefactor, accepted the duty to protect you from harm.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_1: See, the Merciful, full of thought to prevent you from seeing harsh realites.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: You, the Unable, Unaccepting to not trek further.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_3: You, may not see it all.
